author: COMSOL
description: This example extends the Large Eddy Simulation of a Sports Car model to include a vibration analysis of a car door with window and rear view mirror. The forces from the fluid interacting with the car body are extruded onto a geometry of a car door and transformed to the frequency domain with FFT.
